ok, i tried that one, but no luck. still nobody cares. so it's that one:
  if (int_status == 0xff) { /* card may be ejected */
        DEBUG(3, "%s: interrupt %d for dead card\n", dev->name, irq);
        handled = 0;
        goto leave;
    }
but it's not ejected, only a modpobe -r...
